      <title>《人人都是产品经理——写给产品新人》</title>
      <link>https://rosefinch-midsummer.github.io/zh/posts/book/%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E7%BB%8F%E7%90%86%E5%86%99%E7%BB%99%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA/</link>
